          <title>Bears fire coach Matt Eberflus after skid marked by poor decisions late in games</title>
          <description><![CDATA[CHICAGO (AP) — Matt Eberflus was fired by the Chicago Bears on Friday, one day after botching a timeout in a loss at Detroit. Offensive coordinator Thomas Brown will serve as interim coach, the Bears said in a statement.]]></description>
